verbose_text: In the nucleus beta-catenin integrates with transcription factors T cell factor 4/lymphoid enhancer binding factor 1 (TCF4 / LEF1) to initiate transcription of Wnt / beta-catenin signaling responsive genes, such as c-myc and cyclin D1, which are key regulators of cell cycle and cell growth.
